TITLE: Verifying Purchases with Adjust Android SDK
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to use the purchase verification feature in the Adjust Android SDK. This is done by calling the verifyPurchase method on the Adjust instance.
SOURCE: https://github.com/adjust/android_sdk/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md#2025-04-22_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: Java
CODE:
```
AdjustPurchase purchase = new AdjustPurchase(price, currency, transactionId, itemSku);
Adjust.verifyPurchase(purchase, new OnPurchaseVerificationFinishedListener() {
    @Override
    public void onVerificationFinished(AdjustPurchaseVerificationResult result) {
        // Handle the verification result
    }
});
```

